track_notes:
I parked in the large layby at SD 973597 to complete the circular walk (Note side trip to garden centre cafe after activation at SD 978602). 
If you wish to go directly to the summit and back as quickly as you can you could park in the small layby at SD 971583 instead.
Direct up and back route. From the cafe car park it took 45 minutes to ascend and 35 minutes to descend with a light pack for VHF only.
track_title: Cracoe Fell from the farm shop - cafe car park in Cracoe

track_notes:
Park at wide lay-by at Rylstone.  Track follows road south but a better option would be the footpath east to the church then south, avoiding the busy road.

Descending from the obelisk requires crossing the wall on the steps and heading north east and not following the wall east.

Cracoe to Rylstone along the farm track is well off the road and a pleasant walk to finish.

Total time (including ops): 1h 20m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T1. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards. Additional route information may be available at www.m1hax.uk. Track data by Richard M1HAX licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA.
track_title: Cracoe Fell from Fell Lane. Sep 2023.
